data.description: This 4-bed, 2.5-bath Hartselle gem is a canvas for your style. With a 20x40 inground pool, privacy-fenced yard, and a covered patio, outdoor living is a dream come true. The 2-story layout features a stunning stone wall gas log fireplace in the living room with bedrooms upstairs. An attached 2-car garage adds convenience & additional storage. Your personal touch will make this house your perfect home.
